Developed by [['Geneering Products]], '''OV600''' was a powerful truth serum often used by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. Unlike other serums such as [[Bavo Six]], OV600 acted physically upon the victim, rather than mentally. When the serum detected the symptoms of lie-telling, it caused the victim's flesh to break out in a painful rash. The serum was powerful enough to cause death in severe cases.

